text:
Okay so! Don't know how good will I do this job of pouring out what my heart has in its stores for you, but since we're huge fans of communicating and expressing, I'll definitely give my best shot. 

First sem ke starting ke bulla sessions me I recognised your presence ki okay ye koi hai. Ye wing ki us side me rehta hai aur ye batti ka hai, to isse jaan pehchan hone wali hai. Kisi point pe hum log saath me batti ki classes ja rhe honge, mug rhe honge, marva rhe honge. Pehla solid interaction first sem ke end me hua. Raat ke 1:30-2 baje kareeb jab wing me sab idhar udhar the, na jaane kaise Kudrat ke Khel se mai, tu aur moond mere kamre me mile. Hum teen, sirf hum teen aur sach batau to me vo Spiderman wali meme jaisa moment hua batti, batti, batti uske baad humne spi puchi ek dusre se aur realise kiya ki kya mast chudi hui batti rhe hum. Mujhe yaad hai hamari spi AP bana rhi thi, mai ye nhi likhunga yaha first term kiska tha aur kya value thi uski ЁЯШВ

Beech me kitne aur moments hain. Summer ka eco101 chaapke CPI 0.4 badhvana, 202, 203 me gaand ka brahmaand hona, but 21 Jan 2019 ko humari paathshala ka banna life defining moment hoga. Bohot khush hota hu aaj bhi maine Atif ko us group me add nhi kiya. Starting me us group ki kuch baatein jaise notes banayenge regular... ЁЯдг Badhiya hai, vhi baatein dekh ab yaad aa rhi.. fourth sem ke courses yaad aate hain. Control ki vo matlab ki quiz yaad aati hai. 201 yaad aata hai. Uske end sem ki pichli raat ke nazare yaad aate hain. Uske baad ki harkate yaad aati hain. Kitna kuch dekha hai tere sath. Digital yaad aata hai. Uske exam ke pehle jo ma chod ke padhe the, (aur chaapu moond ne pata nai sab kab kar liya tha) yaad aata hai.

Summer ke vo sexy discussions. Kya time tha yaar vo. Khud ka gyaan base badhana, TED ka craze, laundo ko kholna, kuch logo ko kuch chijo ki jagah batana ЁЯШВ

Itni chije hain ek ek pe individual essay likh skte hain. CAA-NRC ke time call pe aakrosh nikalna, Airtel walo ka khud call cut kr dena ЁЯШЖ aake moond ki bandi ke saath special date pe jana. CCD pe bill faadna, usse to bohot zada better kr skte the apan. Bad luck! Logo ke upar judgements dena ЁЯШК kuch heart-to-heart secrets, kuch confessions, moond ka unme se kuch bhi nhi samajhna, moond ki pel ke bina unit measurement pe udana.. sab kuch to kr liya tere sath ЁЯзб

As human tere me changes dekhta hu to bohot accha feel hota hai. Chhoti chhoti chije samajhne laga hai tu, bohot mature ho gya hai, emotional, social har type ke scenarios se deal kr skta hai. We know this is not an easy feat. And mai aise sound kr rha hu like mujhe sab kuch aata hai but lol really, noo!!!!! I know and I can tell how much I've grown too in the process. You're an excellent mate! Still waiting for kab tu apne gharwalo ko us chij pe gyaan dega ЁЯШБ

Beech me tough moments aaye, I fumbled, I should have done better but had this strong belief ki it'll pass, we'll hold and come back stronger. And then that's what we did ЁЯТЪ

UPSC clear kr ab jldi se mc, launde ki intern sort krni hai, aur bhi bohot kaam hn plan me jo tere UPSC pe depend krte hain. Aur rishtedaaro ke ghar vo khat bhi to bhejna hai ЁЯШЫЁЯТе

Dhyan rakh, milte hain jldi! тЭдя╕П

text:
Dear Captain 

There's something about you that meeting you felt like an instant hit. A man of integrity, a soul of will, you are fierce, you are ruthless. You're the perfect PR man. But you're so much more than that. Keep your reckless spirit always up! Only you can carry that, folks around need that in you. Vo trihug yaad hai mujhe, I share a bond with you on multiple levels since. Dhyan rakh, milte hain, Ashok ki fuddi bhi krni hai abhi тЭдя╕ПЁЯФе

Pyaare mOOnd! 

Jitna cute tu hai, utni hi teri baatein. Thodi outrageous bhi ЁЯШВ but ab to aadat si ho gyi hai vo 50% illogical, 50% super illogical ki to vhi sunne me accha lagta hai. Accha lagta hai tera kuch na samajhna appear hona, yet ander sab kuch utni hi maturity se deal krna

Daaru peena pata nai kyu tune late start ki. Jaat hai tu, to jldi expect kiya tha тШ║я╕П Abhinav ne to pehle hi laal jhandi de di thi, par tere sath laga tha jldi krenge. And personal sessions rkhenge room me raat me sem ke beech Friday Friday, Abhinav ki observant aankho ke saamne ЁЯШВ. Mujhe tera shirts ka chaska bohot adorable lagta hai. Tu comfort ko itna priority pe rakhta hai ye tere sath rehke us summer me pata chala. Hansta tha mai terko raat me dekhke. Cooler vagaira sab itna pyaar se set krta tha tu. Abhinav ko Ruby bolte hain apan par mai bata rha hu asli nanhi jaan to tu hai ЁЯРг

Ye wala part kabhi bola nhi. Aaj yaha bolta hu. Jldi jldi bolne aur jldi jldi movie dekhne ke alawa tu jldi jldi padhta bhi hai. 370 ke paper ke time hum log last wala part padh rhe the aur tune shayad vo kiya nhi tha. Infact tu aage ka 310 dekh rha tha, and pata nhi baad me tune kaise kiya vo, but sooo proud you did. Good good! тЭдя╕П

Thumbs up ko EXPLOIT kam kiya kar. Try to kar kabhi. Do chaar shabd bolne ka. Once. Just once. Accha lagega. Kabhi vo wali duniya me bhi kadam rakh ke dekh. Kabhi Abhinav ko bhi khush krke dekh ЁЯШЫЁЯШЖ

Ek chij aur dhyan me rakh le. Teri shaadi me drama khada krne wale hn pakka. Pehle hi gharwalo ko aagah kar dena. Aisa na ho talware nikal le vo humpe. Aakhir ghar ke chirag ki shaadi hai, shor sharaba hona to banta hai, phir chahe bhagana hi na pad jaye teri mashuka ko. Planning to us raat board pe bakchod kar hi li thi ЁЯТе

Memes bana yaar aur often. Khud nhi bana rha to taimur wali jaisa content hi de de ЁЯдг btw teri vo bday wali memes pasand aayi thi usko. Also, shukriya posts pe engagement badhane ke liye. Apne bando pe flex krna har kisi ki khushi me nhi ЁЯзб

text:
Aditya Gupta Synchro,
Tera text aaya tha, tujhe synchro ka puchna tha aur as it turns out, mai khud nhi bana uske baad bwahaha ЁЯШЖ. text: Ek ek word jo tune kaha hai core tak hit hua hai. Virtual hi sahi, karani to thi. Aur karayi, puri thok ke! Aur samajh rha hu tera concern yaar. Launde ready to nhi but ragon me aa jayega inke bhi vhi junoon, vhi jo hume bhi fuel kiya tha with almost everything up against! Ek baar on ground wapas aane de. Utar jayenge sab maidan me. Us din aag laga denge Gupta. No mercy khelenge us din. Jo log bhul gye hain thoda bohot, koma me jane ka natak kar rhe hain, unhe koma se nikal ke seedha maut me fenkenge. Beech me brief moment ke liye Antaragni ki aag dikhegi, jo tez hogi itni bhayankar ki sadma lagega bhayanak. MI ka to khel khatam kar hi chuke hain is baar. 4-5 aur edition aise nikal denge to khatam hai scene phir. Raaj hoga, Tanashahi chalegi. Chalegi jab tak hain apan jaise launde. Antaragni yaha se aur ruthless hi hogi Gupta, vaada hai mera terko yaha is memoirs ke jahan par! Ye sari memories hongi ek taraf, aur Antaragni ke 4 din ek taraf ЁЯФе

text:
Are oh kalakaar

Pence ke aane se pehle ka vo time, aisa lag rha tha bas theher jaye vo. Itna sahi lag rha tha. Ghabra rhe the apan shit ki teesra kaisa hoga, na hi aaye to behtar hoga. Par accha hi hua pence aa gya. Apan dono ko vrna BT me beh jane se kon rokta. Time to time apan pe check kon krta ЁЯШВ 

Pata nhi exam time pe aisa kya hota tha jop duniya jaha ki sari BT tabhi hit krti thi. Ruka hi nhi jata tha, kar hi lete the intense discussions, jab tak do chaar logo/ systemo ko galiya nhi dete the wapas padhai ho nhi pati thi

Tere sath ekdum mast tuning thi. MTH ke bhi lectures kaise to vo tutorials se paar kiye the apan ne. Tu room ka DJ ban jata tha, ekdum sahi mood pakadke gaane lagata tha. Room ki harmony itni pyaari thi, ki us chakkar me vo gate pe antigens wala message chipka diya tha ЁЯШВ

Pata hai tujhe dekhta hu apni kalakaar zindagi jeete hue, apni hi dhun me mast, to shayad tujhse kai zada khushi mujhe hoti hai ЁЯШД starting me thoda inhibited sa tha tu, but vo galaxy ke time jab nukkad me jaane lage tu aur pence, aur room wapas aake adhip chitral ko galiya galiya ke "nukkad nhi krunga", "dobara kabhi nhi krunga", vo ek do baar ka pura brainfuck ke baad, to jaise tu alag hi haseen ho gya, apni kala me kho gya, hum sabko moh gya ЁЯТЪ

Tu kehta hai bro mai change ho gya. But agar tere jaisa hi change hai ye to to sahi hai phir. Nukkad ko khudka aur khudko nukkad ka hamesha ek hissa banaye rakhna bro. You stay so pure, so true to your art! Ek dusre ke pehle dost the iitk me. Rhenge last tak, abhi tere aur kirdaar dekhne hain baaki тЭдя╕П

author: Jai Ranjan Sharma

text:
Careful Jay. It's Ms Flamme here. 

Jab starting me aaya tha to itni entropy expect nhi ki tha. Silly me? Haan partly. College me aa rhe ho, how do you expect everything to go so nice n cheese, but spare me thoda sa, mai itna bhi guilty nhi because aane ke 2-3 din me hee ek ladki se milna hua. Vo mere bagal me hi baithi thi, sab theek tha, itne me hi vo achanak meri taraf mudi, aur ek shabd boli. Ek, sirf ek. Samajh to nhi paya mai us samay kya hua, kya ho gya. Samajh to aaj bhi nhi paya hu par us shabd ki uttejna usi pal se alag ho gyi zindagi bhar ke liye. Usne kajal lagaya tha, badi hi pyaari lag rhi thi vo.

Tujhe yaad hoga ki humne numbers exchange nhi kiye the bade time tak. Mudreka ke thru milte the, hawa ki philosophy discuss krte the. God ki existence ko brutally destroy aur defend kiya. Self ki depths ko, heights ko, beliefs ko, connects ko, sab kuch test hua, sab kuch test kiya. Discussions bohot hue. Aur in sab ke beech pata chala tu jitni thoughts me rebel hai, utni hi life me bhi.

Tu ye jaanti hogi Gunjan ki walks pe bohot saari mast crazy baate ki, par tu ye nhi jaanti hogi ki in walks ke pehle mai padh ke aata tha, prepare krke aata tha. Tujhe ye realisation hoga Gunjan ki teri company special to thi, par tu ye nhi jaanti hogi ki isse pehle kabhi itna tense nhi hua. Tu shayad is chij se bhi aware hogi Gunjan ki tere liye vo poem ek din me likhi thi, par tu ye nhi jaanti hogi ki us din ke baad mai aajtak koi poem complete nhi kar paya. Bohot attempts liye, abhi bhi ek pe kaam kr rha par yet koi complete nhi kr paya. 

2nd year me aaye, milna kam ho gya. Jaha hafte me roz milte the aur 2-3 baar ghumne chale jaate the, vaha ab dikhna bhi naseeb me nhi hua. Tu padhai me dhyan laga rhi thi, mai pata nhi kya kr rha tha. Time tha, time kam nhi pada par ye bhi sach hai ki hum nhi mile itna jitna pehle milte the.

Nhi socha tha ye gap badhta hi chala jayega. Beech beech me sparks the. Diro bungalow ke bahar us raat ki light setting imprinted hai man me, rhegi aur anant tak. Vo chaurahe ke aage road kinare mandir se emanating green light yaad hai? Tune hath pakad ke aur dara diya tha. Baate jab bhi hui tere sath, acchi hui. It's hard to find koi aur un baato ke liye. Kam hone lagi, par vo elements the. Vo glory thi. Shayad apne apne raaste pakad liye. Antaragni ho gyi, mere bahane khatam. Ek din room pe aya tere. Us din samajh aayi. Baat kr rhe the, teri aankhein nam ho gyi. Mujhe maaf krna Gunjan. I learnt life me kuch us din. Won't go down that fucking lane ever again. 

Mai kabhi concede nhi krna chahta, na krunga ki tu cute hai. Par ab samajh gya hu. Pehle mai delusional tha, ab denial me hu. Tu hai cute, aur nhi bhi. 

If there's a bond I care and value about so much in my life, it's with you. Abhi bhi waaqif nhi ise kya kehte hain, but the day it comes to it, I'll put up a good fight, take note of that! Hey, aisa ho skta hai ki kinhi moments me dikhe nahi, but stay there na, call me up, and ask me blunt up front. I'll take responsibility of rest. 

Listening to T wala song. You're the one, suit, for it. Ms Flamme, ЁЯТЪ
author: Jai Ranjan Sharma

text:
To the one I know I can always count upon. Kaha se shuru kruu. Kaise sab bayan kru. Kisi ne mujhe puri is journey me itna closely dekha hai. Kaise use uski yaari ada kru..

Vo likhta hu jo feel krta hu tere around. Kyunki instances to itne hain tere saath ki ek din bhi utha lu koi, to bhi sharma jayega ye memoir.  

Tere around galti krne se dar nhi lagta. Tere around kuch try krne se dar nhi lagta. Vo chahe kuch naya ho ya 100vi baar vhi purani chij jise sab logo ne khaarij kr diya. Bada bhai type nhi bolta hu thoda scenty ho jayega ЁЯШЕ but ek warmness ka blanket lagta hai.. ki it's okayyy. Go ahead. Pence hai na. 

Terse bht kuch seekha hai. I can count it on fingers un logo ke naam for whom I have soo much respect when it comes to work ethic. Shayad tujhe dekh ke hee to mujhme bhi thoda sa aaya hai ye. I think vo beds sath sath hone ka kamaal hai ye sab ЁЯЩГ

Positivity aur confidence ki to jaise khadaan hai tu. And vo bhi non-exhaustible. Infact lag rha ki time ke saath saath iske reserves aur badhte hi jaa rhe. Always keep it up! People need it. You're the one. You be there for everyone! 

Aati hai baat teri shaadi ki to know this. Ofcourse teri marzi ke against kuch nhi hoga but I'll give you a worthy fight brother ЁЯЩВ you have my word on it. And you know why I push it so much, because it's sooo important for your growth. You HAVE to have it. Pleeeaaaaase!

You have embarked upon a very brave journey. I love you. Dhyan rakhna. Sambhal ke. You know the code. Put it into work. I have wild faith that you'll soon break into big big headlines. And loads and loads of riches! Is memoir ko likhne ke duration me memories saari tatol rha tha. To vo 'Chakravyuh me fans gye hain hum' wala gyaan yaad aya. Soch ke hi smile aa gyi chehre pe thinking shayad hamara ek saathi finally free ho gya hai us bandhan se. Felt so elated, so puffed, so proud ЁЯзб

Trips pe chal yaar bohot saari. Bohot saari. Acche logo ka sirf saath hona kaafi nhi, bht saari acchi memories bhi chahiye unke saath. Mumbai-Pune trip jaisi countless more intense escapades chahiye and with apni puri gang. Maza aa jayega bc jldi chalooo 

Recently abhi misidentified the author of some certain words. Cool hai. Nice kind reminder that it's always work in progress ЁЯШД And so I have to continue digging, and so I will ЁЯЩВ

Bas saath rehna Pence. Zindagi bhar. Sach kahu to tujhse itna attached ho gya hu ki chhotu aisa lagta hai mera hi chhota bhai hai. Hence thappad maarne ka man karta hai use all the more vo sab chindi harkato me indulge hote dekhke ЁЯШВ Thappad as in ofcourse figuratively. Like what big brothers are for ЁЯдО 

Behne ka time kareeb hai lag rha, to rakhta hu ab apni kalam ye. Pence.. you got my back always, I hope to be in that same role for you too. Lots of love, dhyan rakh, aur jldi mil 

With ЁЯТЪ
J.

text:
Are oh Hero!

Synchro starting yaad hai? Neeche F1 me call karne aate the sab apan Vivek ke room. Gaand fati me tu bahar chale jata tha. Vivek starting me majak udate the par tera kala jaadu zada strong tha. Tu wapas I'd leke hee aata tha ЁЯШВтЭдя╕П 

Yaaaaaar, synchro ka vo tenure zindagi bhar ki memories hai. Teen dildaar dost, ek anokha mentor. Kya nhi kiya saath. Maine kabhi nhi imagine kiya tha Apr me vo starting me, ki ye journey is tarah jaayegi. Kaam ke waqt kaam, bakchodi ke waqt bakchodi. Beer peene jate the saath gate par. Aate the cycle pe, Vivek mast mast gyan dete the. Apan hanste the. Party gang ban gyi thi apni. 

Vivek ke saath anban bhi hui. But wapas sort kr lete the. Antaragni ke vo 4 din to jaise amar hee ho gye apan aur apna synchro. Synchro stage pe chadhe to the par feeling udne wali thi. Pata nhi aisa kya kar diya tha, chehro pe badi si muskurahat aur dil me itni khushi. Sach me laga us din Rock immortal ho gyaa ЁЯдШЁЯФе

Uske baad apni baari. Chaap diye sab ek baar phir. Pata tha rukna nhi tha waha. Ek akhiri aur baar krni thi Antaragni. Aa jata bro saath, miss kiya tujhe bohot. Start hone se pehle hee janta tha miss krunga. But khush hu ki tune apna time liya, jis purpose se gya tha vo pura kiya. Aur wapas aaya. Dil le le bro, hamesha saath rehna. Kala ke saath rhega tu to ughh aaunga campus to milenge. Bade din hue, jarurat hai dil ki, fir maahol jamayenge, aur nayi yaade banayenge ЁЯФе

Aur saale vo Milgram experiment abhi bhi gaand me ghusa hua hai. Kya kiya tha aisa bhai ЁЯШВ

Dur rehke aalsi ho gya tha bas tu, par last ke dino me tujhe wapas maidan me dahadte dekh purane dino ki yaad aa gyi jab darindagi se kuch nhi chora tha apan ne. Ek baar phir sab kuch fateh kar liya, phir charo or jhande gaad diye, itihaas likh diya.. naam kama liya, shauhrat bhi aur sath sath izzat bhi ЁЯФе

Beer ki jagah daaru thi hath me, aur ujale ki jagah andhera. Par yakeen maan dil me jaise ek nayi mashaal jal gyi us raat. Dosti ki nayi gehraiyan choo li. Ehsaas hue naye kuch khaas. Us raat mujhe ek khayal aya. Yadu, tu jaan maang lena, de dunga.. par kabhi Jai ki dosti mat todna. Mat chorna kabhi saath,
